{
  "id": "kn-story-001",
  "title": "The Thirsty Crow",
  "title_kn": "ಬಾಯಾರಿದ ಕಾಗೆ",
  "tier": 1,
  "description": "A classic Panchatantra tale about a clever crow who finds water using stones.",
  "sentences": [
    { "kn": "ಒಂದು ಬೇಸಿಗೆಯ ದಿನ.", "en": "One summer day.", "tr": "Ondu bēsigeya dina.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_0.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_0.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಒಂದು ಕಾಗೆ ಹಾರುತ್ತಿತ್ತು.", "en": "A crow was flying.", "tr": "Ondu kāge hāruttittu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_1.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_1.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಾಗೆಗೆ ತುಂಬಾ ಬಾಯಾರಿಕೆ ಆಗಿತ್ತು.", "en": "The crow was very thirsty.", "tr": "Kāgege tumbā bāyārike āgittu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_2.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_2.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಾಗೆ ನೀರು ಹುಡುಕಿತು.", "en": "The crow searched for water.", "tr": "Kāge nīru huḍukitu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_3.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_3.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಎಲ್ಲಿಯೂ ನೀರು ಇರಲಿಲ್ಲ.", "en": "There was no water anywhere.", "tr": "Elliyū nīru iralilla.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_4.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_4.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಾಗೆ ತುಂಬಾ ದಣಿದಿತ್ತು.", "en": "The crow was very tired.", "tr": "Kāge tumbā daṇidittu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_5.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_5.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಆಗ ಕಾಗೆಗೆ ಒಂದು ಮಡಕೆ ಕಾಣಿಸಿತು.", "en": "Then the crow saw a pot.", "tr": "Āga kāgege ondu maḍake kāṇisitu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_6.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_6.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಮಡಕೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಸ್ವಲ್ಪ ನೀರು ಇತ್ತು.", "en": "There was a little water in the pot.", "tr": "Maḍakeyalli svalpa nīru ittu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_7.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_7.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಆದರೆ ನೀರು ತುಂಬಾ ಕೆಳಗೆ ಇತ್ತು.", "en": "But the water was very low.", "tr": "Ādare nīru tumbā keḷage ittu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_8.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_8.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಾಗೆಯ ಕೊಕ್ಕು ನೀರನ್ನು ಮುಟ್ಟಲಿಲ್ಲ.", "en": "The crow's beak could not reach the water.", "tr": "Kāgeya kokku nīrannu muṭṭalilla.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_9.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_9.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಾಗೆ ಯೋಚಿಸಿತು.", "en": "The crow thought.", "tr": "Kāge yōchisitu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_10.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_10.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಾಗೆಗೆ ಒಂದು ಉಪಾಯ ಹೊಳೆಯಿತು!", "en": "The crow had an idea!", "tr": "Kāgege ondu upāya hoḷeyitu!", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_11.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_11.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಾಗೆ ಒಂದು ಕಲ್ಲು ತಂದಿತು.", "en": "The crow brought a stone.", "tr": "Kāge ondu kallu tanditu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_12.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_12.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಲ್ಲನ್ನು ಮಡಕೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಹಾಕಿತು.", "en": "It dropped the stone in the pot.", "tr": "Kallannu maḍakeyalli hākitu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_13.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_13.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ನೀರು ಸ್ವಲ್ಪ ಮೇಲೆ ಬಂತು.", "en": "The water came up a little.", "tr": "Nīru svalpa mēle bantu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_14.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_14.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಾಗೆ ಇನ್ನೊಂದು ಕಲ್ಲು ಹಾಕಿತು.", "en": "The crow dropped another stone.", "tr": "Kāge innondu kallu hākitu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_15.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_15.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಇನ್ನೊಂದು. ಇನ್ನೊಂದು. ಇನ್ನೊಂದು.", "en": "Another. Another. Another.", "tr": "Innondu. Innondu. Innondu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_16.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_16.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ನೀರು ಮೇಲೆ ಮೇಲೆ ಬಂತು.", "en": "The water came up and up.", "tr": "Nīru mēle mēle bantu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_17.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_17.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕೊನೆಗೆ ನೀರು ಮೇಲೆ ಬಂತು!", "en": "Finally the water reached the top!", "tr": "Konege nīru mēle bantu!", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_18.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_18.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಾಗೆ ನೀರು ಕುಡಿಯಿತು.", "en": "The crow drank the water.", "tr": "Kāge nīru kuḍiyitu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_19.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_19.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಕಾಗೆ ತುಂಬಾ ಖುಷಿಯಾಯಿತು.", "en": "The crow was very happy.", "tr": "Kāge tumbā khushiyāyitu.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_20.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_20.mp3" },
    { "kn": "ಬುದ್ಧಿ ಇದ್ದರೆ, ದಾರಿ ಸಿಗುತ್ತದೆ.", "en": "Where there is a will, there is a way.", "tr": "Buddhi iddare, dāri siguttade.", "kn_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/kn_21.mp3", "en_audio_url": "/audio/stories/kn-story-001/en_21.mp3" }
  ]
}
